subject: R
object: So, Sally and Anne, let's start building the tracks. I count on you guys. Are you ready? Also, you need to play this game together, as both of you will see different views at all times. You can talk now to help each other. To see my instructions again, check the information icon on your screens. Time to play. Let's Go!

subject: R
object: You are not that far from the minimum; the difference is only 7 Francs. I am sure you can do it.

subject: R
object: By the way, you guys now also have the button on the bottom of your screen in the abstract view for comparing solutions.

subject: R
object: So guys,..You have 5 more minutes to find the best solution. You can do it!
